column5: .....dont shoot the messenger.  Glad I pushed my trip back. Wow.  http://www.algonquinpark.on.ca/news/2014/spring_2014_update.php
Thanks for the update , glad my back country trip isn't planned until the second week of May. One good thing is no chance of black flies and it will be perfect timing for the lake trout bite !
Saw that, we are booked in from may 10-17 along the Nippissing from Brent. Got my fingers crossed we'll get in. This weather is not helping
That's late. Fishing should be good!
Well ther goes my trip for May 5th-9th. Looks like I be going 12-16.
